Package: remotes
Title: R Package Installation from Remote 'GitHub' Repositories
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Gabor Csardi, Hadley Wickham
Maintainer: Gabor Csardi <gcsardi@mango-solutions.com>
Description: Download and install R packages stored in 'GitHub',
    repositories. This package is a lightweight replacement of
    'devtools::install_github()'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/mangothecat/remotes
BugReports: https://github.com/mangothecat/remotes/issues
Suggests:
    BiocInstaller,
    covr,
    testthat
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
